  <ul>
    <li><strong>Jupyter Notebooks</strong> — Core agent workspace</li>
    <li><strong>Docker</strong> — Secure, containerized execution</li>
    <li><strong>RPy2, IRKernel</strong> — First-class R support</li>
    <li><strong>Fern</strong> — Robust SDK tooling</li>
    <li><strong>Arrow, Parquet</strong> — Efficient data transport and storage</li>
    <li><strong>Jamsocket</strong> — High-reliability execution backend</li>
    <li><strong>Matplotlib, Plotly</strong> — Trusted visualization libraries</li>
